                <head>No. 61<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>Among the letters exchanged between the three Foreign Ministers and the Federal
                    Chancellor on May 26 was a letter concerning the entry into force of the
                    contractual agreements. For text of this letter, see item 2 of the minutes of
                    the meeting of the Foreign Ministers with Chancellor <persName corresp="#p_AK1"
                        >Adenauer</persName>, <ref target="#d48">Document 48</ref>.</p>
            </div>
